Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.38,0:00:32.18,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,不死樹
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.22,0:00:34.68,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,何為真相
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.93,0:00:38.64,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,我將成為真相
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.19,0:00:49.61,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,我看到那片光亮
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.57,0:00:55.95,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,這就是我的全部
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.66,0:00:58.41,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,你說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.62,0:01:00.50,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.12,0:01:05.09,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,你為什麼說
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.30,0:01:10.59,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,磨刀 小憩
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.59,0:01:13.80,OP-CH,,0,0,0,,生存之景
